thread.title: Danny N.

author: Danny N.
title: Danny N.
text: Very impressed with their services and will recommend other business associates to Havealook. What impressed me most was that Havealook had members attend our office for our own convenience who explained, in detail, the website building process step by step. What was even more convenient was Havaelook's website building set-up sheets which contained tutorials of what material and information they required from us. Having previously engaged a website designer who did not deliver on my expectations, the systems and processes that Havealook have implemented ensured that my website building process was seamless. They've definitely done this before. Again, to the team at Havealook thank you!
